M|Chec|For |
M|Chec|tx|**New Employee Onboarding Checklist**
M|Chec|it|[ ] Equipment ordered (IT, day -7)
M|Chec|it|[ ] Accounts created (IT, day -3)
M|Chec|it|[ ] Welcome em sent (HR, day -1)
M|Chec|it|[ ] Office tour (Manager, day 1)
M|Chec|it|[ ] Core values training (HR, day 1)
M|Chec|it|[ ] Process training begins (Manager, day 2)
M|Chec|it|[ ] 30-day check-in scheduled (Manager, day 1)
M|The |1. *|** New hire observes an experienced team member performing the process
M|The |2. *|** New hire performs the process w/ the experienced team member coaching
M|The |3. *|** New hire explains the process back to someone else
M|The |tx|If they can teach it, they know it. This method works for any process in any department.
M|Trai|tx|\| Week \| Focus \| Method \| Assessment \|
M|Trai|tx|\|------\|-------\|--------\|------------\|
M|Trai|tx|\| 1 \| Company overview, core values, core processes overview \| Orientation sn \| Can state core values and name all core processes \|
M|Trai|tx|\| 2 \| Primary process (the one they will use daily) \| See-Do-Teach \| Completes process independently w/ <2 er \|
M|Trai|tx|\| 3 \| Secondary processes (ones they interact w/) \| See + doc rv \| Can explain how their work connects to upstream/downstream processes \|
M|Trai|tx|\| 4 \| Edge cases and exceptions \| Scenario-based practice \| Handles 3 of 4 edge case scenarios correctly \|
M|Quar|Ever|
M|Revi|1. *|** Are people following the process? Where are the deviations?
M|Revi|2. *|** Is the process producing the desired outcomes? What do the Scorecard metrics say?
M|Revi|3. *|** What feedback have we received? What steps shd be added, removed, or changed?
M|Proc|tx|\| Process \| Compliance Rate \| Outcome qual \| Last Updated \| Status \|
M|Proc|tx|\|---------\|---------------\|-----------------\|-------------\|--------\|
M|Proc|tx|\| The rv Engine \| 85% \| Win rate 28% \| Jan 15 \| Healthy \|
M|Proc|tx|\| The bd Cycle \| 70% \| On-time 82% \| Dec 1 \| Needs attention \|
M|Proc|tx|\| The People Path \| 90% \| 90-day retention 95% \| Jan 20 \| Healthy \|
M|Proc|tx|\| The Care Loop \| 60% \| CSAT 3.8/5 \| Oct 15 \| At risk \|
M|Proc|tx|\| The Money Flow \| 95% \| AR <30 days 92% \| Jan 10 \| Healthy \|
M|Proc|tx|Any process below 80% compliance or w/ declining outcome qual goes to the Issues List for IDS.